  "keyFeatures": [
    "Physics-based contraption assembly via the Physics Assembler block",
    "Flying vehicles using Hot Air Burners, Propeller Bearings, and Levitite",
    "Ground vehicles with Wheel Mounts and tire items",
    "Swivel Bearing for rotating physics contraptions",
    "Rope Winch and Rope Connector for tethering contraptions",
    "Sensors: Altitude, Velocity, Optical, Laser, Gimbal, Navigation Table",
    "Redstone automation: Accumulator, Inductor, Magnet, Throttle Lever",
    "Borehead Bearing for drill-head excavation contraptions",
    "ComputerCraft peripheral support for all major sensor blocks",
    "Levitite Blend — a crystallizable anti-gravity fluid"
